<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[الآيات الواردة في <span class="c2">«الأثرة»</span>]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١- فَإِذا جاءَتِ الطَّامَّةُ الْكُبْرى <span class="c2">(٣٤)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَوْمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنْسانُ ما سَعى <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَبُرِّزَتِ الْجَحِيمُ لِمَنْ يَرى <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَأَمَّا مَنْ طَغى <span class="c2">(٣٧)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَآثَرَ الْحَياةَ الدُّنْيا <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَأَمَّا مَنْ خافَ مَقامَ رَبِّهِ وَنَهَى النَّفْسَ عَنِ الْهَوى <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَإِنَّ الْجَنَّةَ هِيَ الْمَأْوى <span class="c2">(٤١)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢- قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَنْ تَزَكَّى <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَذَكَرَ اسْمَ رَبِّهِ فَصَلَّى <span class="c2">(١٥)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>بَلْ تُؤْثِرُونَ الْحَياةَ الدُّنْيا <span class="c2">(١٦)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَالْآخِرَةُ خَيْرٌ وَأَبْقى <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) النازعات: ٣٤- ٤١ مكية<br>(٢) الأعلى: ١٤- ١٧ مكية</p> </div>